name: Askthelabratwhathe'sthinking
0:
”Alexa, ask the lab rat”
”Alexa, ask the lab rat are you thinking what I am thinking.”
”Alexa, ask the lab rat are you pondering what i am pondering”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the lab rat
des: This skill returns a random thought from the lab rat to make sure you guys are on the same page. Just say, Alexa, ask the lab rat. and then she will ask you what you want to ask, and then you can ask, are you thinking what I'm thinking?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
